lenders.name: Suzanne
lenders.loan_because: Vesta, the ancient Roman Goddess of Fire and Hearth, provides nourishment, warmth and home through her eternal flame.  We, at Vestaweavers International Knitworks, hope to inspire endless compassion, abundance, warmth and home through our textiles.  We are proud to report we have arrived at our objective to pay forward 100% of the profit made through the sales of our knitworks in direct support of cultural development grants to individuals and small communities in need.  We thank Kiva for the assistance in making this goal a reality.
lenders.occupational_info:
People have adorned themselves with glass, metals and textiles for centuries. These elements carry the powers of the universe: strength, wisdom, healing, abundance and love. Vestaweavers International knitworks impart these and many more of the life forces that inspire us to feel at the core of our being.

I am so grateful for the opportunity to spread the elemental energy of these wraps to people already wearing and enjoying them in Spain, Italy, England, China, Japan and Central America as well as cities throughout the United States. I am thrilled to continue to illuminate the beauty, peace, hope and love that they imbue.

Vestaweavers International Knitworks wraps wearers around the world with the one energy that ignites and connects us all.
